@startuml
actor "Usuario Comercial" as Usuario
participant "Comercial UI" as UI
participant "ComercialController" as Controller
participant "ComercialService" as Service
participant "ApplicationDBContext" as DB
participant "PdfService" as Pdf

Usuario -> UI : Rellenar formulario de cotización
UI -> Controller : POST /Comercial/Cotizacion/Create
Controller -> Service : CrearCotizacion(model)
Service -> DB : Guardar Cotizacion
DB --> Service : Cotizacion guardada
Service -> Pdf : GenerarCotizacion(cotizacion)
Pdf --> Service : byte[] PDF
Service -> Controller : Resultado + PDF
Controller -> UI : Mostrar confirmación / enlace descarga
@enduml